          <p>
            <span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><img alt="" src="https://goto.msstate.edu/www/images/Distance/Application/email%20-1.png" style="width: 750px; height: 422px;" /></span>
          </p>

          <div>
            <span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Hey, @@{{Preferred}}!</span><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"></span></span></span></span></span></span><br />
            <br />
            <span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Are you thinking about earning your degree online?&nbsp; Summer 2021 is the perfect time to start! If you complete your Summer 2021 <b></b>application by <b>Friday, February 26, 2021</b> you will be eligible to earn BullyBundles!&nbsp; Click</span></span><a href="https://www.apply.msstate.edu/" style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">here</span></span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">to apply.</span></span></span></span></span><br />
            <span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br />
            <b><span style="color:#660000">What is a BullyBundle?</span></b><br />
            A BullyBundle is an assortment of Mississippi State Online items including pens, tech items, and more!<br />
            <br />
            <b><span style="color:#660000">How do I earn a BullyBundle?</span></b></span></span></span></span></span>

            <ol>
              <li style="margin-bottom:11px">
                <span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><a href="http://www.apply.msstate.edu/" style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline" target="_blank"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:#660000">Apply for admission</span></span></span></a><b>&nbsp;</b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">by <b>Friday, February 26, 2021</b> for the Summer 2021 semester. Once you have completed your application, you'll get your first BullyBundle!&nbsp;<br />
                &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span>
              </li>
              <li style="margin-bottom:11px">
                <span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:#660000">Get admitted!</span></span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">Once you have been accepted as a Mississippi State University student, you'll get your second BullyBundle!<br />
                &nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span>
              </li>
              <li style="margin-bottom:11px">
                <span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="tab-stops:list .5in"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:#660000">Enroll</span></span></span></b><b></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">in <b>Summer 2021</b> courses! Once enrolled in courses for the <b>Summer 2021</b> semester, you'll receive your final BullyBundle after the semester begins!</span></span></span></span></span></span>
              </li>
            </ol>
            <span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><span style="color:#660000">When will I get my BullyBundle?</span></span></span></b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif"><br />
            BullyBundles will be mailed out the week the first week of March.&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />
            <br />
            <i>*Only those seeking an online undergraduate or graduate degree who apply for Summer 2021 admission through</i><b>Friday, February 26, 2021</b><i>will be eligible for BullyBundles.</i><br />
            <br />
            We look forward to helping you achieve your educational goals!&nbsp;<br />
            If you have any questions, please email them to&nbsp;</span></span><a href="mailto:mindy.wolfe@msstate.edu" style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">mindy.wolfe@msstate.edu</span></span></a><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">.</span></span></span></span></span><br />
            <span style="font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif;"><br />
            <strong>Mindy Wolfe</strong><br />
            <em>Recruitment Coordinator</em><br />
            <a href="mailto:mindy.wolfe@msstate.edu">mindy.wolfe@msstate.edu</a><br />
            Mississippi State University Online<br />
            <br />
            Follow us on social media! #msstateonline | #hailstatefromanystate<br />
            <br />
            <img alt="" src="https://goto.msstate.edu/www/images/Distance/msstate_online_horizontal.png" style="width: 624px; height: 87px;" /></span>

